40萬掩口費嫌貴壓價<br />\n<br />\n該周刊亦聲稱擁有C朗同代表律師奧蘇里奧（Os&oacute;rio de Castro）嘅聯絡短訊，顯示C朗喺2010年得知被控後積極尋求庭外和解，當時對方開出95萬美元（約740萬港元）掩口費，C朗得知後大發雷霆表示費用過高，要求律師討價還價，最終以大約4折即37.5萬美元達成協議。"},{"pid":"91830995594280450ddaa685b393ba8d376d080c","tid":605700,"uid":33789,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"自從當年我朗炒鳩垃圾拜仁之後,樓主就顛9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怨婦"},{"pid":"da2e865c3b5bb811c52c7cdd5a6598ee67a724ce","tid":605700,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91830995594280450ddaa685b393ba8d376d080c","tid":605700,"uid":33789,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"自從當年我朗炒鳩垃圾拜仁之後,樓主就顛9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怨婦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"傷人<br />\n逃稅<br />\n強姦<br />\n衰11<br />\n超速<br />\n開淫P<br />\n斷背<br />\n恐嚇<br />\n勒索<br />\n衝紅燈<br />\n非禮<br />\n性騷擾"},{"pid":"fdf7e879e3fdabf057c03a2c8d5ac09bc0b3ecdf","tid":605700,"uid":33660,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"91830995594280450ddaa685b393ba8d376d080c","tid":605700,"uid":33789,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"自從當年我朗炒鳩垃圾拜仁之後,樓主就顛9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怨婦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:36:41.000Z","msg":"呢個就真係強姦喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5baa8563e806357b07e4abd6b1c99a745d385cd","tid":605700,"uid":141824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我朗"},{"pid":"fc651d7311ada50fa9023272f8ed1a9de4f0a1de","tid":605700,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca004b7b3e5e5fa2d8d3aacf9593f2c43dbfb4b5","tid":605700,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e